Title says all :D
It took us 1 hour+ of constant fighting and dedication to create the largest skybridge ever seen on nebula ever seen by the players! Thanks to lime team it reached off the map and was extended almost over the entire map, at least over 50%. If you have a screenshot or video please post it below :D! This is avicus wise

Builders: GrapeSmoothie, Zerkk, Iron, Jahaj and the effort of both teams!
